interestingcomments.content: First trip with my new R6
interestingcomments.MarkedSent: First trip with my new R6

interestingcomments.content:
EOS Road Trip /!/ The EOS road trip has to be the greatest but worst thing ever for us amateur/hobbyist photographers. 

I just had my session today. 

R6 + 70-200 f2.8. 

Man I have some serious GAS right now when sitting here staring at the photos I took on the R6 and my RP sitting on my desk beside me 😂. 

If anyone hasn’t had a chance to check out a EOS Road Trip session I’d say do it up. Right now it’s just R5/R6 but soon they’ll have the R3 (likely next years Road Trip).
